## VHWDA Project Rules (Agent Guidance)

### Design tokens
- Never hardcode colors; use CSS variables from `tokens.css` (e.g. `var(--color-...)`) and reference them via Tailwind theme tokens.

### Localization
- All user-facing strings must go through i18n utilities. Do not inline English strings in components except as translation keys or fallback values inside the i18n layer.


